:3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"唔借"},{"pid":"fe46adedeba81e743d58c0ec237bd8a87f580157","tid":271810,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"係女既就請佢一齊食"},{"pid":"baf56eee23c1b8b70455863f90ac7378b24d1e3b","tid":271810,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借定送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話就話借 但都預左唔還 <br />\n講比好似老馮咁 咪講借好似好聽d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890de5f37e0636e3964812e2db040183881bada9","tid":271810,"uid":111286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"試過 但發現佢地係呃人<br />\n我個陣係兩個大陸人講話比人偷左銀包 <br />\n佢地好肚餓 問我可唔可以買水同包比佢食<br />\n之後我見又唔係問我拎錢 直接買野食咪買比佢囉 個十蚊八蚊<br />\nDllm 之後去seven 愈買愈多 最後又話要買煙 我即刻話食咩野煙呀<br />\n最後都買左50幾蚊野食<br />\n佢地態度好誠懇嫁 <br />\n又話叫你比電話遲下請你食番餐好 話自己大陸好有錢<br />\n我幫佢又唔係為報答 所以冇比到電話<br />\n最後一路行一路諗覺得好奇怪 <br />\n心諗我依區好少有遊客<br />\n上網一check 先發現好多人都遇過<br />\n大家巴絲唔好上當！<br />\n雖然錢唔算多 但比人昆一蚊都厭多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家google 下會搵到多d資料"},{"pid":"3ca8f625ae478b35e808da75c9e13ddee5862d87","tid":271810,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過 但發現佢地係呃人<br />\n我個陣係兩個大陸人講話比人偷左銀包 <br />\n佢地好肚餓 問我可唔可以買水同包比佢食<br />\n之後我見又唔係問我拎錢 直接買野食咪買比佢囉 個十蚊八蚊<br />\nDllm 之後去seven 愈買愈多 最後又話要買煙 我即刻話食咩野煙呀<br />\n最後都買左50幾蚊野食<br />\n佢地態度好誠懇嫁 <br />\n又話叫你比電話遲下請你食番餐好 話自己大陸好有錢<br />\n我幫佢又唔係為報答 所以冇比到電話<br />\n最後一路行一路諗覺得好奇怪 <br />\n心諗我依區好少有遊客<br />\n上網一check 先發現好多人都遇過<br />\n大家巴絲唔好上當！<br />\n雖然錢唔算多 但比人昆一蚊都厭多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家google 下會搵到多d資料</blockquote><br />\n我都遇過係外國道友借錢<br />\n話借&pound;1 打電話 之後𥄫到佢冇打電話 最後我望到實先扮下野打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之後急急腳走 我行入去電話停先發現...<br />\n打個電話唔洗&pound;1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到我之後都唔知借唔借好 <br />\n如果真係有事 唔借又好衰仔<br />\n比人呃又唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c64f626e2ce26905fe338b62abc542aed2a5b4","tid":271810,"uid":80664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"假架，中左一次伏 $50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed183276f7fddd1c7b73149158fe543a7cad0d2","tid":271810,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"如果係樓主情況緊係ok <br />\n但現實都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45910dea30d43643e5775a0b154135362edcd60d","tid":271810,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係樓主情況緊係ok <br />\n但現實都唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔係我遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a28ac5e814518883302a88d36f1df11662e9923","tid":271810,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"我屌你個非洲呀，我巴西嫁碌柒"},{"pid":"0f073488dd13df48e4babc0b9f0b1209fc8fa0cf","tid":271810,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"錢你老母包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bfab548bfe48f7